    VadereBuilder provide methods to manipulate the attributes/parameters of a scenario. It's an interface for generate multiple Vadere-Scenario based on the same infrastructure but with different attributes/parameters. The class does not provide methods to change the infrastructure of the Topography. To use this effectively the user need a good knowledge about the parameters of the given scenario!
